job summary
the data scientist analyzes design implement and evaluates business process and data to develop insight and predictive analytics of the company operation and competitive strength this position is responsible for developing cutting edge predictive model that drive service strategy and operation performing data analysis developing algorithm and predictive model and presenting technical information to a broad audience additionally the data scientist will apply algorithm and modeling tool to business data and develop solution in collaboration with our people business partner and customer
principal accountabilities
interact directly with business partner to support their operational need enabling the business to make effective decision and solve problem with quantified insight into data
gain an understanding of business process problem and question translating issue into requirement that can be understood and executed efficiently and effectively and maintaining constant communication with business partner in order to follow-up and validate result and or answer question
develop statistical model methodology to predict quantify and or forecast various business metric
develop and maintain a suite of predictive analytics to drive business engagement in service activity
perform hands-on data manipulation transformation hypothesis testing and predictive modeling
evaluate refine and continuously improve the efficiency and accuracy of existing predictive model
ensure and maintain data quality and reliability
identify and recommend new data source that will maximize analytic output and create customized report dashboard with a team of analyst and developer
collaborative on insight with other data scientist business intelligence developer business analyst and business partner
creatively communicate and present model to business partner and executive utilizing a variety of format and visualization methodology
champion new innovative idea around the data science and advanced analytics practice
ensure full and clear documentation of all process
